DescriptionText.SourceString: The Moon saves you from the poison. "What were you thinking? Back to Bed!" he screams. Everything fades to black.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The Moon saves you from the poison. "What were you thinking? Back to Bed!" he screams. Everything fades to black.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The Moon comes out of the darkness of the cave. "Not now. I'm too busy! Back to Bed!" Everything fades to black.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The Moon comes out of the darkness of the cave. "Not now. I'm too busy! Back to Bed!" Everything fades to black.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The nest is empty.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The nest is empty.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You find a Chica Party Time Cup in the nest!
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You find a Chica Party Time Cup in the nest!

DescriptionText.SourceString: The nest is empty.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The nest is empty.

DescriptionText.SourceString: A lizard, a squirrel, and a snake are having a tea party. Nothing unusual.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: A lizard, a squirrel, and a snake are having a tea party. Nothing unusual.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The branch is too thick. You can't break it.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The branch is too thick. You can't break it.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You saw the branch off with your knife. You now have a walking stick!
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You saw the branch off with your knife. You now have a walking stick!

DescriptionText.SourceString: You take the Chica Cup.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You take the Chica Cup.

DescriptionText.SourceString: Outside your house. There's a scary tree and a path running east and west.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: Outside your house. There's a scary tree and a path running east and west.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The soup tastes strange, like plums and nutmeg. The world spins, and the last thing you see is the Moon above...
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The soup tastes strange, like plums and nutmeg. The world spins, and the last thing you see is the Moon above...

DescriptionText.SourceString: You pour the soup into the cup. It's warm in your hands.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You pour the soup into the cup. It's warm in your hands.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You walk towards the cave entrance. A cold, angry wind brushes past you, but you continue inside...
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You walk towards the cave entrance. A cold, angry wind brushes past you, but you continue inside...

DescriptionText.SourceString: A Starbright Night Light. It takes the firelight and burns forever.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: A Starbright Night Light. It takes the firelight and burns forever.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You stand in front of a dark, scary cave, with a campfire out front. Above the fire is a bubbling cauldron that holds an odd smelling soup.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You stand in front of a dark, scary cave, with a campfire out front. Above the fire is a bubbling cauldron that holds an odd smelling soup.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The Oak Tree groans. It seems to be in pain.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The Oak Tree groans. It seems to be in pain.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You walk up and examine the Oak Tree.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You walk up and examine the Oak Tree.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The Oak Tree groans. It seems to be in pain. It looks like a knife is sticking out of the side.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The Oak Tree groans. It seems to be in pain. It looks like a knife is sticking out of the side.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You find a Ranger Army Knife! The tree sighs and smiles. It's much better now.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You find a Ranger Army Knife! The tree sighs and smiles. It's much better now.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You say hello to the Oak Tree. It smiles and thanks you again.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You say hello to the Oak Tree. It smiles and thanks you again.

DescriptionText.SourceString: A forest path leads deeper into the night. A very happy Baby Owl hoots and flies around your head.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: A forest path leads deeper into the night. A very happy Baby Owl hoots and flies around your head.

DescriptionText.SourceString: A forest path leads deeper into the night, but it's blocked by a Gator who is trying to eat a Baby Owl.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: A forest path leads deeper into the night, but it's blocked by a Gator who is trying to eat a Baby Owl.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The Baby Owl coos and flutters his wings.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The Baby Owl coos and flutters his wings.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You take the path deeper into the forest.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You take the path deeper into the forest.

DescriptionText.SourceString: The Gator snaps at you. You back off.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: The Gator snaps at you. You back off.

DescriptionText.SourceString: You throw the Chica cup at the Gator. He eats it and dies.
DescriptionText.LocalizedString: You throw the Chica cup at the Gator. He eats it and dies.
